<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>PRAISE HIM! PRAISE HIM!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pak un! pak un, Lal Isu I Tanpau deihum!
 Simlei, la sa'n, A hehpih mak phuong un;
 Amah chawian hen, van Angel lienpen inle,
 Hatna, zahna A min thiengtho piei tiu,
 Belampu bang' Isu'n A mite A pui,
 A chawnban in nitum in A veng hi.

[V2]
 Pak un! Pak un!
 A lopina chungnung phuong un;
 Pak un! Pak un! kipahna la'n sau in!

[V3]
 2. Pak un! Pak un! Lal Isu I Tanpau deihum!
 I gitloh ziek un A thuok in, A thi'i;
 Amah Suongpi, kumsawt hukdamna kinepna,
 Chawian un! Isu khetden a um chu!
 Pakna la sau, Isu'n I lungkham A puo'i,
 Tawpbei hehpihna thuk leh mak A nei.

[V4]
 3. Pak un! Pak un! Lal Isu I Tanpau deihum,
 Thangvan tuol ah, 'Hosanna!' ti'n a sau;
 Lal Isu Hukdampa'n kumkhuo'n vai A hawm hi,
 Pak un! Amah Thiemgau, Thiempu, Lalpen!
 Khawvel zawhna tawh Krista lei ah hung ding,
 Hatna leh lopina Lalpa chang hen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>33</hymn_number>
</song>